    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其 10 月份贸易逆差缩小 13%，进口降幅放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/turkey-trade-deficit-narrows-13-in-october-import-drop-slows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其 10 月份贸易逆差为 57.5 亿美元，进一步收窄表明该国经济的再平衡仍在进行中。进口降幅为过去六个月来最慢，反映出土耳其里拉的相对强势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/turkey-trade-deficit-narrows-13-in-october-import-drop-slows</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Nov 2024 09:48:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
